<l>kaṇṭā ruyiruṇṇun tōṟṟattāṟ peṇṭakaip</l>
<l> pētaik kamarttaṉa kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These eyes that seem to kill those who look at them are as it were in hostilities with this feminine simplicity.</l>
